      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "xjL1l",
          "fill": "#3D3D3D",
          "content": "交互说明 ③",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "LUqfL",
          "fill": "#2D2D2D",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 358,
          "content": "• 翻译底卡从底部滑入，相机始终可见\n• 当全部文字翻译完毕后，译文自动播放朗读翻译\n• 下滑 → 关闭底卡，返回①\n• 上滑拖动把手 → 全屏查看详细翻译 进入5页面",
          "lineHeight": 1.4,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "kPXMx",
      "x": 1260,
      "y": 920,
      "name": "note_menu",
      "width": 390,
      "fill": "#F7F3ED",
